  <brief_title>Endosponge Vacuum Therapy (E-VAC) Registry of Intestinal Anastomotic Leaks and Perforations</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Registry The Treatment Of Upper And Lower Intestinal Anastomotic Leaks And Perforations</official_title>
